Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.30,中文,,0,0,0,,《僵尸国度》前情提要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Previously on Z Nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:04.07,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦 是个活生生的婴儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Whoa. It's a real live baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.11,0:00:06.14,中文,,0,0,0,,别抱得像是抱个活生生的手榴弹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't hold him like he's a live grenade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:07.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我跟婴儿并没有那么亲近\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Me and babies, not so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.18,中文,,0,0,0,,我们在执行一个至关重要的任务\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're on a high priority mission
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:15.28,中文,,0,0,0,,要把这个人护送到加州的疾控中心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to get this man to a CDC lab in California.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:17.69,中文,,0,0,0,,一些衣衫褴褛的烂平民群体不得不引起担忧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can't worry about some raggedy ass group of civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:21.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我们并不是什么衣衫褴褛的烂平民群体 长官\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing raggedy ass about this group of civilians, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:22.19,中文,,0,0,0,,放松点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:23.56,中文,,0,0,0,,加内特和沃伦知道他们在做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Garnett and Warren know what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:42.35,中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,586)}{\fs50\fn微软雅黑\bord1\b1\fsp20}伊利诺斯州南部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:52.79,中文,,0,0,0,,来 给\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:55.06,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 亲爱的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah, thank you, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:01:00.16,中文,,0,0,0,,恩恩 没什么比早上来一杯咖啡更好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mmmm-mmm. Nothing like the first cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:06.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我跟你的止痛药\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I will see your vicodin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:08.27,中文,,0,0,0,,再加一颗四环素\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and raise you one tetracycline.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.04,中文,,0,0,0,,叫牌\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:13.34,中文,,0,0,0,,3个K\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Three of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:14.71,中文,,0,0,0,,满堂红\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Full house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:16.21,中文,,0,0,0,,A最大咯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aces high.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:17.18,中文,,0,0,0,,老兄\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:19.28,中文,,0,0,0,,你已经连赢五把了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's five hands in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:21.92,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你还想继续用我的桌子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you're gonna continue to use my deck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:24.02,中文,,0,0,0,,那你就别再从屁股里掏牌了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you need to quit pulling cards out your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.05,0:01:25.12,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 哟哟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Oh boo hoo. -
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:27.96,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘘  等下 市民Z回线上了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey shhh. Hold on, he's back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:30.89,中文,,0,0,0,,小伙伴们 我想说的是 恶劣天气马上来袭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Friends, I'm talking about mean weather coming in fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:32.36,中文,,0,0,0,,有报道说是龙卷风\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Some reports of tornados.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:33.93,中文,,0,0,0,,找到庇护所快躲躲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Find shelter and take cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:36.50,中文,,0,0,0,,在外面很危险 比往常来说更危险\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's dangerous out there. More so than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:40.67,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我为大家放一曲灾难前暖心的歌曲听听吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now back to the soothing sounds of the Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.38,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 在他搞错了直升机的事儿后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know after he was so wrong about that chopper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:51.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得天气预报的活儿挺适合他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}weatherman's a pretty good job for that geek.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:51.84,中文,,0,0,0,,轮到你们了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:52.84,中文,,0,0,0,,没事儿吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:53.94,中文,,0,0,0,,平静的一夜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Peaceful night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:55.84,中文,,0,0,0,,你的脑残粉说马上会有风暴来袭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your stalker said there's a storm front coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.74,中文,,0,0,0,,外面有迹象吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How is it out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:01:59.58,中文,,0,0,0,,乌云满布 也有可能是僵尸来袭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Cloudy with a chance of zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:01.78,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 你俩去休息吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, you two get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:03.85,中文,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:16.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我曾经过过更差的生活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've had worse days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:18.56,中文,,0,0,0,,这也不能算差吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not a bad set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:20.67,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mmm-hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:27.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.51,中文,,0,0,0,,我真的开始觉得这里有点家的感觉了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm really starting to feel at home here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我在考虑在这里搞一个烧烤摊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm thinking about putting a barbecue right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:37.72,中文,,0,0,0,,要先把这东西清理一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This one needs to be flipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:51.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我真的很喜欢屋主的这些布景 这些花儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I really like what they did with the landscaping, the flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.23,中文,,0,0,0,,所有东西 都特别有家的感觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}everything. So homey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.54,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 只可惜他们都死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah. Too bad they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.64,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:03.71,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.98,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起 进错房间了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry. Wrong room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:10.78,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:15.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天 是床  上次我们在床上做是多久之前了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh my God. A bed. When was the last time we did it in a bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.59,中文,,0,0,0,,全裸咩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.29,中文,,0,0,0,,把衣服都脱了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Like no clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.70,中文,,0,0,0,,一丝不挂好嘛 宝贝儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Full commando, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天  你还真是浪漫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh my God, you are such a romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.12,中文,,0,0,0,,这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.25,中文,,0,0,0,,毛毯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}blanket...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.69,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.42,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.90,中文,,0,0,0,,真怕那家伙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Scared of that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:00.13,中文,,0,0,0,,最好就是甭惹她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Best not to mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:04.44,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 如果我们好好培养下那两个 僵尸可有的受了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know if we breed those two, it'd be all over for the zombies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:13.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我记不得上次偷偷和别人溜出来是什么时候了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can't remember the last time I snuck off with somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我根本记不得上一次有这个念头是什么时候了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't remember the last time I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:32.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你仍想着他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You still think about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.67,中文,,0,0,0,,安托万吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Antoine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我尽量不去想他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I try not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:40.91,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不知道后来发生了什么 所以也还好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I never heard what happened, so there's not much point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.88,中文,,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:46.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我曾经每天都想艾米和孩子们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I used to think about Amy and the kids everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:50.52,中文,,0,0,0,,每当我闭上眼 分别时的场景就历历在目\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Every time I closed my eyes, I saw the end all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.55,中文,,0,0,0,,到了一定程度 我就放弃了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It got to a certain point where I just gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:56.39,中文,,0,0,0,,不去在乎我自己是死是活\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Didn't care if I lived or died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.89,中文,,0,0,0,,有趣的事儿就出现了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And a funny thing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我没死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:06.40,中文,,0,0,0,,那么多事发生了后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And with everything that's happened
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:10.34,中文,,0,0,0,,记住过去变得越来越难\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it's been harder and harder to remember the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我想那是件好事儿 不是吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I guess that's a good thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.67,中文,,0,0,0,,但愿吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我们是不是离你家乡很近\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are we close by your hometown?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:24.22,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你在想什么 答案是 不行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know what you're thinking, and the answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:25.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我们往西走的时候顺便拜访一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just swing by on our way west.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:28.89,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么 都已经过去很久了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why? It's long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.52,中文,,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:37.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我只希望当时候我能等等他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I just wish that I would've waited for him
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:42.53,中文,,0,0,0,,在最后一次出发之前能跟他好好的道别\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and said goodbye before the last time I got shipped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.34,中文,,0,0,0,,你不想去确认下吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't you want to know for sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:49.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你自己都不确定的事 你就没有办法去忘记\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You can't start forgetting what you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.81,中文,,0,0,0,,这看起来可不妙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That does not look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.22,中文,,0,0,0,,这是龙卷风\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's tornado weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.53,中文,,0,0,0,,龙卷风要来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.28,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.81,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.18,中文,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:31.55,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:32.89,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.52,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.34,中文,,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:05.45,中文,,0,0,0,,阿猫阿狗们 该走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Puppies and kittens! Time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:09.42,中文,,0,0,0,,所有人从后门出去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Everybody out the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:24.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我来帮你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I give you mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.31,中文,,0,0,0,,{\pos(664,512)}{\fs50\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\fsp20}北极光基地\N国家安全局指挥中心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:57.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我讨厌盲点 伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I hate blind spots, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.50,中文,,0,0,0,,让我焦虑啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Make me anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.31,中文,,0,0,0,,都消化不良了呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mess with my digestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:06.18,中文,,0,0,0,,真有趣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:21.56,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起 我忘了你了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry, I forgot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.50,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 对了 你在戒酒呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh that's right, you're on the wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:33.71,中文,,0,0,0,,对不起 我忘了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:38.18,中文,,0,0,0,,比独饮独酌更惨的就是不能喝酒了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The only thing worse than drinking alone is not drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:46.92,中文,,0,0,0,,美女你好啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello, beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:48.19,中文,,0,0,0,,咱们是要找什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are we looking at here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.90,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.30,中文,,0,0,0,,厉害啊 龙卷风走廊果然名不虚传\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dang. They don't call it Tornado Alley for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我没喝醉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I am not drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.47,中文,,0,0,0,,你才喝醉了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:10.61,中文,,0,0,0,,你全家都喝醉了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, your mom's drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:27.76,中文,,0,0,0,,为了持续为您带来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In our continuing effort to bring you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.30,中文,,0,0,0,,最新消息 我们僵尸电视台调用了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}up to the minute information, we at Z-TV have acquired
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.30,中文,,0,0,0,,一颗被弃用多时的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a National Weather Service satellite
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:33.97,中文,,0,0,0,,气象局卫星信号\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that they aren't using anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.50,中文,,0,0,0,,但这都不是重点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But that's not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:38.30,中文,,0,0,0,,现在镜头转向南方天气预报员约翰 史密斯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We now go to John Smith, southern weather correspondent
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:41.31,中文,,0,0,0,,听听他的意见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to get his opinion on the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:44.71,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我这么多年来见过最强的风暴了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is the badassest storm this weatherman has ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:47.95,中文,,0,0,0,,从墨西哥湾一直延伸到密西西比河谷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}From the Gulf of Mexico right up the Mississippi Valley,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.25,中文,,0,0,0,,麻烦临头咯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}trouble is brewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道该叫他飓风还是龙卷风\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know if they call this thing a turricane or a tornado
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:55.15,中文,,0,0,0,,还是别的什么 但是只要你在芝加哥南边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or what. But if you're anywhere south of Chicago
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.42,中文,,0,0,0,,或者落基山东面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or east of the Rockies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:10:00.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我可得警告你们 赶快躲起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm issuing a get your butt in a bunker warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我希望你们几个能听到这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, I hope you guys are getting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:05.16,中文,,0,0,0,,安迪和小伙伴们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Addy and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.57,中文,,0,0,0,,你们得赶紧找地方躲起来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You guys got to seek shelter immediately because
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:10.60,中文,,0,0,0,,这风暴很厉害 还有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}this is bad. And
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.50,中文,,0,0,0,,你们马上去找避难所\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}when you seek shelter immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.57,中文,,0,0,0,,找到过后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and after you do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:16.24,中文,,0,0,0,,你们马上联系我告诉我你们的位置\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you need to contact me and tell me where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:20.41,中文,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你接下来该怎么做 好咩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And I'll update you with further instructions. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:24.25,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 我是市民Z 播报完毕\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right, well this is Citizen Z, and I'm signing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.95,中文,,0,0,0,,谁是安迪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who's Addy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:29.99,中文,,0,0,0,,接下来我们走哪条路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So which way do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.59,中文,,0,0,0,,风暴从墨西哥湾向北推进\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The storm is pushing north from the gulf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.33,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们能走上70号公路 就可以躲过风暴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If we make it to the I-70, we can outrun it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.96,中文,,0,0,0,,这风暴科比破卡车快多了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That storm is going faster than that craptastic truck ever will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:38.73,中文,,0,0,0,,是的 我们不能在大路上走了 你听见市民Z说的了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, we got to get off the road. You heard Citizen Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:39.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得去找避难所\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We got to seek shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我们现在需要做的就是逃离这个鬼地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What we need is to get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我可不会因为那个卫星小子说了两句就不走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I ain't stopping just cuz some punk with a satellite says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:47.27,中文,,0,0,0,,慢着 我听错了什么吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, hang on. Am I missing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你们大老远把我拽过来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You did not drag my ass this far
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.39,中文,,0,0,0,,可不是为了让龙卷风把救世主吹到天上吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so that mankind's hope could get sucked up by a tornado,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:53.16,中文,,0,0,0,,是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.56,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 安迪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, Addy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:58.73,中文,,0,0,0,,你一直不说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know you've been quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是想确认你是否还好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just want to make sure you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.20,中文,,0,0,0,,恩 我还好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.54,中文,,0,0,0,,只是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Just,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.50,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道的 僵尸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you know, zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.88,中文,,0,0,0,,有谁有薄荷糖吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Anybody got a mint?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:35.70,中文,,0,0,0,,卡斯尔伯恩特 那是你家乡是吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Castle Point. That's your hometown right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:46.44,中文,,0,0,0,,哇哦 看 风暴来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Whoa. Look at that storm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:50.05,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 你赢了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, fine. You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:17.84,中文,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家 罗伯塔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Welcome home, Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.08,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你对这个小镇很熟吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you know this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:24.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我在这里出生长大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Born and raised here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.94,中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要避一避\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We need to take cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:50.74,中文,,0,0,0,,这附近有什么安全的地儿吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is there someplace safe nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:53.24,中文,,0,0,0,,有我家有个防风窖\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, there's a storm cellar in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.71,中文,,0,0,0,,你家离这有多远\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How close by is your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.28,中文,,0,0,0,,不算远\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:59.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我认识这些人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I knew these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:02.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我的邻居\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:04.89,中文,,0,0,0,,上司\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.93,中文,,0,0,0,,我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.60,中文,,0,0,0,,是他吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.80,中文,,0,0,0,,他是谁\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who's him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.77,中文,,0,0,0,,噢 不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:26.61,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不是来找你死去的丈夫的 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. We are not here searching for dead hubby, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:28.21,中文,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:30.15,中文,,0,0,0,,避难所在这边\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shelter's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:36.42,中文,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:38.32,中文,,0,0,0,,真绿啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's so green.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.33,中文,,0,0,0,,我从来没见过天空这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I never seen a sky look like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.49,中文,,0,0,0,,我只在电视上见过龙卷风\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've only seen tornadoes on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢龙卷风\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't like tornadoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:47.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我想它们也不待见我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm pretty sure they don't like me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.47,中文,,0,0,0,,那个吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.37,中文,,0,0,0,,就是那个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:28.24,中文,,0,0,0,,一万 快来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}10K, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:38.05,中文,,0,0,0,,快开啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:51.96,中文,,0,0,0,,如果他在里面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If he's in there and he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:53.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我会毫不犹豫的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I will not hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:41.25,中文,,0,0,0,,家有僵尸的感觉真好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Home sweet zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.65,中文,,0,0,0,,从椅子上滚下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get out of that chair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:45.38,中文,,0,0,0,,你快给我滚开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go on and get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:48.22,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我老公最喜欢的椅子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's my husband's favorite chair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:50.49,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.26,中文,,0,0,0,,呃 楼上安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh, upstairs is all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.17,中文,,0,0,0,,让我来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:15.71,中文,,0,0,0,,请不要开枪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Please don't shoot us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我丈夫受伤了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My husband is hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.65,中文,,0,0,0,,你在我家里干什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are you doing in my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:24.39,中文,,0,0,0,,有个消防员说我们在这里会很安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The fireman said we'd be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:34.87,中文,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.23,中文,,0,0,0,,像狂犬一样吠叫吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bark like a dog for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:40.44,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧我刚不是对你说的 不过我很感动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well I wasn't talking to you, but I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:44.64,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:47.65,中文,,0,0,0,,从三级风暴变成七层地狱了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}From a Category Three to the Seventh Circle of Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:51.32,中文,,0,0,0,,三角洲X光小队 希望你们大家伙儿不在那片乌云底下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Delta-Xray-Delta, I hope you guys aren't underneath that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:53.79,中文,,0,0,0,,快啊 给我个信号\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come on. Drop me a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:56.25,中文,,0,0,0,,放个照明弹 给我个电话 什么都行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Send up a flare. Give me a ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.59,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我找不到你们 我是帮不来了你们的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't help you if I can't find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:02.99,中文,,0,0,0,,你会没事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:04.86,中文,,0,0,0,,他是个医生\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:05.90,中文,,0,0,0,,额\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:08.43,中文,,0,0,0,,他们只是这么叫我而已\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}well they sorta just call me Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:09.87,中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:13.00,中文,,0,0,0,,不需要医生 我只要睡一会儿就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No doctor. I just... need a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.47,中文,,0,0,0,,哦内什么 那可不行 老兄\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh that, no that wouldn't be good, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.51,中文,,0,0,0,,千万别睡过去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do not nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:21.51,中文,,0,0,0,,别让他睡着 他至少是脑震荡了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't let him fall asleep. He's got a bad concussion at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.92,中文,,0,0,0,,里克 里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rick? Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:25.48,中文,,0,0,0,,快救救他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:29.85,中文,,0,0,0,,地下室安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Basement's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.66,中文,,0,0,0,,他不会有事吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is he gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:35.93,中文,,0,0,0,,是这个消防员吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is this the fireman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:36.76,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:40.67,中文,,0,0,0,,是这个消防员带你们来这儿的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is this the fireman that brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.23,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.54,中文,,0,0,0,,也许吧 他当时头上戴着头盔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe. He was wearing a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.41,中文,,0,0,0,,可能就是他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得就是他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.78,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:12.26,中文,,0,0,0,,暴风雨来之前 我们要离开这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We need to get out of here before this storm hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:17.02,中文,,0,0,0,,那去哪儿呢 哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And go where, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.02,中文,,0,0,0,,那我们怎么办 坐以待毙吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are we supposed to do, just sit heres cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:19.52,中文,,0,0,0,,地下室是安全的 我们可以下去避一避\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The basement is secure. We can ride it out down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我们只要在暴风雨来之前 找够必须的物资就好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's just gather some supplies before it hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.26,中文,,0,0,0,,厨房里有不少必需品呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kitchen was pretty well stocked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:25.60,中文,,0,0,0,,有水和罐头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's water and canned food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:27.60,中文,,0,0,0,,不过没有医疗用品 也没有电池\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No medical supplies, no batteries though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.27,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要和外界取得联络\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We need to get our communications up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.87,中文,,0,0,0,,你们俩 去周围找找看\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You two, go out in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.87,中文,,0,0,0,,看能找到些什么 但别走远\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}See what you can find. But don't go far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:34.97,中文,,0,0,0,,一定要在暴风雨来之前赶回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Be sure to get back before the storm hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:39.11,中文,,0,0,0,,詹妮 这些人在这里干什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Janey what are all these people doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:41.78,中文,,0,0,0,,我爸妈马上要回家来吃饭了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My parents will be home for dinner any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.11,中文,,0,0,0,,他能撑过去吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is he gonna make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:46.78,中文,,0,0,0,,你是问真的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that a serious question?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:47.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.25,中文,,0,0,0,,他脑袋上裂了个大窟窿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He got cracked on the dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.39,中文,,0,0,0,,好了 至少我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay, I for one
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:52.52,中文,,0,0,0,,不想和这家伙一起困在地下室里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}do not want to be trapped in a basement with this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.39,中文,,0,0,0,,他的大脑要开始尸化了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}when he starts craving brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.06,中文,,0,0,0,,别理他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't mind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:59.36,中文,,0,0,0,,他老妈从没好好教他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}His mama didn't raise him right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:02.57,中文,,0,0,0,,最好我有药品 或者急救箱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well if I had the proper meds or a first aid kit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:06.57,中文,,0,0,0,,消防站可能还有急救用品\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know the fire station may still have first aid supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.67,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:09.74,中文,,0,0,0,,把地下室锁好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}lock down the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:12.24,中文,,0,0,0,,如果那小子开始尸化 我要你立刻处理掉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If that kid turns, I want you to be right on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:13.51,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 当然\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:16.88,中文,,0,0,0,,看好墨菲 暴风雨开始之前我们会回来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep an eye on Murphy. We'll be back before the party starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.63,中文,,0,0,0,,艾迪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Addy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:35.00,中文,,0,0,0,,艾迪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Addy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:39.97,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:40.77,中文,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.17,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:43.11,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:33.79,中文,,0,0,0,,这地方勾起了好多回忆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This place brings back so many memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.19,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:39.70,中文,,0,0,0,,我初吻的地儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My first kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.03,中文,,0,0,0,,和那个消防员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}With the fireman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:42.17,中文,,0,0,0,,安托万 是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Antoine, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:42.93,中文,,0,0,0,,当心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:48.17,中文,,0,0,0,,直到现在我才想起那个初吻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I totally forgot about that kiss until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:51.01,中文,,0,0,0,,那一定是牛逼的一吻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That must have been some kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:53.81,中文,,0,0,0,,那可不仅仅是一个吻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was more than just a kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.71,中文,,0,0,0,,那个吻是爱的诠释\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was a kiss that explained things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都无法用语言来表达\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We couldn't seem to say to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:01.45,中文,,0,0,0,,看看你这大情圣\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look who's the big romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:06.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得这是你对我讲的第一件私事儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I think that's the first personal story you ever told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:07.99,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I loved that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:10.99,中文,,0,0,0,,这边走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:31.38,中文,,0,0,0,,看起来很久没人来过了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Doesn't look like anybody's been here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:32.88,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:38.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我们看看能找到什么好东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Let's find what we can and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:42.56,中文,,0,0,0,,急救箱 看起来不错\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}First aid kits look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.83,中文,,0,0,0,,没用过的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hardly touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.17,中文,,0,0,0,,还有些吗啡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Even some morphine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.84,中文,,0,0,0,,别跟医生讲哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't tell Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:05.75,中文,,0,0,0,,他可能还在这里的哪个地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know he could still be around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.39,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:14.99,中文,,0,0,0,,两年前的新泽西之战 我把这张照片寄过来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I sent this after the Battle of New Jersey two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.03,0:22:18.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我们差点就能说当面说再见了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Closest we got to a goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:22.43,中文,,0,0,0,,他执勤那天 我离开了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I deployed while he was on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.07,中文,,0,0,0,,我应该等他回家的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I should've waited for him to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:27.04,中文,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:33.01,中文,,0,0,0,,肯定有人住过你家里 厨房里有储备\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Someone's living in your house. The pantry's stocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:35.95,中文,,0,0,0,,那小俩口也说见过一个消防员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That couple said they met a fireman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:40.45,中文,,0,0,0,,有可能他还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There's a chance he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:44.49,中文,,0,0,0,,没希望了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That life is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.52,0:22:47.56,中文,,0,0,0,,很早之前我就知道了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've known that for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:00.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我们时间不多了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:04.34,中文,,0,0,0,,找地方避避 快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Shelter! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.31,0:23:51.04,中文,,0,0,0,,选择去留吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Pick your poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.07,0:23:52.71,中文,,0,0,0,,里面比外面安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's safer in here than out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:54.64,中文,,0,0,0,,好 你看到他了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Okay. Do you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:56.45,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我们面对的是一群死人了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's the living against the dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:23:57.68,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.71,0:23:58.88,中文,,0,0,0,,子弹用完了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.92,0:23:59.65,中文,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.60,0:24:20.07,中文,,0,0,0,,你后面\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.92,0:24:33.65,中文,,0,0,0,,安托万\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Antoine?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.68,0:24:34.58,中文,,0,0,0,,当心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.29,0:24:44.59,中文,,0,0,0,,安托万\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Antoine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.63,0:24:45.43,中文,,0,0,0,,是他吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.23,0:24:46.73,中文,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.56,0:24:50.30,中文,,0,0,0,,是他的最好朋友\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, it's his best friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.80,0:24:53.40,中文,,0,0,0,,迪尔伯恩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dearborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.44,0:24:55.10,中文,,0,0,0,,马特·迪尔伯恩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Matt Dearborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.14,0:24:57.91,中文,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.94,0:24:58.71,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.74,0:24:59.71,中文,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.93,0:25:21.10,中文,,0,0,0,,轻点儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Easy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.13,0:25:22.60,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.63,0:25:25.03,中文,,0,0,0,,跟外面那些兄弟会的小子说 快关掉死亡金属乐 吵死了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tell those frat boys out there to turn down the death metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.07,0:25:26.30,中文,,0,0,0,,不然我又要叫警察来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll call the cops again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.34,0:25:27.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我会说的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.24,0:25:29.81,中文,,0,0,0,,这老兄的大脑在充血 快崩溃了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The dude's brain is getting crushed by the swelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.84,0:25:31.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要想办法降低脑压\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We need to relieve the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.81,0:25:33.14,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 我们该怎么做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Great. How we gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.18,0:25:34.54,中文,,0,0,0,,额 我不知道具体的方法\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh, I don't know exactly. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.58,0:25:36.65,中文,,0,0,0,,不过我在一集《急诊室的故事》里看到过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I saw this once on an episode of ER.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.68,0:25:39.31,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要把大脑里的血抽出来 我想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We need to drain the blood out I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.35,0:25:41.68,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我们要找个尖尖的锋利的东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So I need something sharp and pointy to...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.72,0:25:43.45,中文,,0,0,0,,比如螺丝锥啊 碎冰锥啊什么的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Like a corkscrew, an ice pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.49,0:25:44.82,中文,,0,0,0,,墨菲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Murphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.85,0:25:47.06,中文,,0,0,0,,墨菲 来帮帮忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Murphy? A little help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.09,0:25:47.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.99,0:25:50.23,中文,,0,0,0,,墨菲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Murphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.26,0:25:53.06,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么回事儿 伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What the hell, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.10,0:25:54.16,中文,,0,0,0,,墨菲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Murphy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.20,0:25:56.10,中文,,0,0,0,,全世界都支离破碎了 伙计\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The world's coming apart around us, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.13,0:25:58.03,中文,,0,0,0,,你还有心情做头发\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And you decide it's time for a haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.07,0:26:00.44,中文,,0,0,0,,不许他靠近里克\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep him away from Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.47,0:26:01.70,中文,,0,0,0,,墨菲 我需要你的帮助\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Murphy, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.74,0:26:04.81,中文,,0,0,0,,找个锋利的东西 我们要切开他的头骨\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Find something sharp to penetrate his skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.48,0:26:08.28,中文,,0,0,0,,要够锋利切开头骨 了解\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sharp enough to penetrate his skull. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.31,0:26:09.64,中文,,0,0,0,,是该把他大卸八块了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}About time we piked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.68,0:26:11.15,中文,,0,0,0,,他在瞎说什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is he talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.18,0:26:12.35,中文,,0,0,0,,开玩笑注意场景好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Way to read the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.38,0:26:13.92,中文,,0,0,0,,他在瞎说什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.95,0:26:17.09,中文,,0,0,0,,别紧张 没人要把你丈夫大卸八块\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't, don't worry. Nobody's gonna pike your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.65,0:26:18.15,中文,,0,0,0,,艾迪去哪儿了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where's Addy?
