Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.83,0:40:19.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道我现在还活着就很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know I'm okay with being here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.60,0:40:20.70,中文,,0,0,0,,和你一起就很好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}With you.
